    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            background-color: white;
            color: black;
        }

        .jumbotron {
            background-color: white;
            color: black;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .section-content {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-custom {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: black;
        }

        .display-4 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .lead {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="jumbotron text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to FinAssist</h1>
        <p class="lead">Manage your finances in an easy and transparent way.</p>
        <hr class="my-4">
        <p>FinAssist is an application that supports household budget management. Its main goal is to make it easier for users to track their expenses. The application allows you to analyze your financial situation in real-time and make informed decisions about managing your household finances based on history and statistics.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="section-title">Main Features of the Application</div>
                <ul class="section-content">
                    <li>Recording income and expenses: Users can add their income and expenses, assign them to various categories, and analyze the cost structure in real-time.</li>
                    <li>History of income and expenses: Every user has access to the history of their income and expenses, enabling detailed transaction monitoring.</li>
                    <li>Generating financial statistics: Users can review monthly reports on expenses, allowing them to identify areas for improvement and better plan their budget for upcoming months.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="section-title">Project Objective</div>
                <ul class="section-content">
                    <li>The main objective of the FinAssist project is to create a platform that helps users efficiently manage their household budget. The application ensures easy monitoring of expenses, planning future payments, and analyzing finances in a clear and intuitive manner. We offer tools to identify areas where costs can be reduced and support planning realistic savings goals.</li>
                    <li>FinAssist is designed for individuals who want to consciously and effectively manage their finances. The aim of the application is to build a habit of regular expense monitoring and saving.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/OperationsModels/UserPanel" class="btn btn-primary btn-custom">Let's begin!</a>
    </div>

    <footer class="text-center mt-5 py-4">
